      <title>罗杰斯以 35 亿美元的价格控制枫叶队和猛龙队</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/rogers-buys-3-5-billion-maple-leaf-sports-stake-sportico-says</link>
